Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reportIlmStatus(25.10)                                  reportIlmStatus(25.10)

Name
       reportIlmStatus  -  Reports  ILM status information including ILM block
       names, ILM data locations, and if the design is in the flattened or un-
       flattened state

Syntax
       reportIlmStatus

       [-help]

       Reports ILM status information including ILM block names, ILM data  lo-
       cations, and if the design is in the flattened or unflattened state.

       You  can  use this command at any time in the flow, but it only reports
       ILM information if you have already specified ILMs in the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the reportIlmStatus command.  For
              a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man reportIlmStatus

Examples
       The   following   command   generates   the   ILM   status  report  for
       dtmf_recvr_core:

       reportIlmStatus

       ==============================================================================

       Current design: dtmf_recvr_core

       Current view is ILM (after flattenIlm)

       Current ILM data is for si mode.

       ==============================================================================

       Cell          Model-Type        Use-Type         Stage         Instance
       Name

       ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

       results_conv      All               ILM                 -           RE-
       SULTS_CONV_INST

       tdsp_core               All                   ILM                     -
       TDSP_CORE_INST

       ILM/flexILM Data Location :

       ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

       results_conv : .../libs/ilm/results_conv.ilm

       tdsp_core : .../libs/ilm/tdsp_core.ilm

       ==============================================================================

